{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"f783e49b1b","title":"日前西方野战军以休养生息为主","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"e739710122","index":0,"year":1936,"month":8,"day":1,"articleId":"f783e49b1b"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji9-1","name":"毛泽东全集第9卷(1)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji9-1.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji9-1":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"e55cfd5f18","type":"paragraph","text":"日前西方野战军以休养生息为主！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"f783e49b1b"},{"id":"84f7a5529b","type":"paragraph","text":"（1936年8月1日）德怀同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"f783e49b1b"},{"id":"49c749192b","type":"paragraph","text":"目前情况下，野战军似宜以休养生息为主，如无充分有利的作战条件，不妨以八月全月为训练时间。从政治的军事的党的各方面进行有计划的教育，务达到一定的进度。一面派出人员从陕甘宁全省进行扩红，后方医院进行治疗改善，以便在八月增加兵员。团以上高级干部宜有特别的教育计划，为将来计，高级干部教育占了特别重要地位。高级教育内容主要的是学习政治。以上意见如得到你的同意，就请你召集团以上干部大会宣布执行。如果我们在八月得到了休养生息的成绩，到九月纪念P二、四方面军南北夹击夺取陕甘大道的战斗，就将更有力量地进行了。如何盼复。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"f783e49b1b"},{"id":"80b6859be1","type":"paragraph","text":"泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"f783e49b1b"},{"id":"2922f70a3d","type":"paragraph","text":"一号十时半","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"f783e49b1b"},{"id":"6ac77fc651","type":"paragraph","text":"[1]这是毛泽东给红军第一方面军司令员、西方野战军司令员兼政治委员彭德怀的电报。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"f783e49b1b"},{"id":"cca23e3db4","type":"paragraph","text":"[2]“纪念”二字似为“配合”之误。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"f783e49b1b"}],"page":{"id":"4f03b536c2","publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"f783e49b1b","start":35,"end":35}}}},"__N_SSG":true}